high_descs: Turn left and walk past the kitchen island, then veer right to the sink.
Pick up the glass in the corner near the microwave.
Talk a step left to the sink.
Wash the glass in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn left an walk ahead all the way to the shelves on the other side of the room.
Place the glass on the shelves, to the right of the dirty plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and move past the white range, then turn right and move to the gray refrigerator, then turn left and face the area of the counter between the sink and the microwave.
Pick up the wine glass to the right of the spoon from the counter.
Move to the sink to the right of the white dishwasher.
Place the wine glass in the sink, rinse it using water from the sink's faucet, then pick up the wine glass from the sink.
Turn left, move past the white range and the green recycling bin on your right, then move to the shelves in the corner of the room past the window.
Place the wine glass on the middle shelf to the right of the dirty blue plate.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned wine glass on the shelf.
